NameValuePair.name: BusinessProcesses/Services/EMAPoller/Query
NameValuePair.value: select /*+ INDEX (EIM_EXECUTED_COMMANDS SPC_TRANS_CMD_X1)*/ ecr.SUBNO SUBNO, ecr.TRANSNO TRANSNO, SUBSTR (TRIM (eec.command), 1, LENGTH (TRIM (eec.command)) - 1)||':TRANSNO,'||ecr.TRANSNO||';' command from EIM_COMMAND_RECORD ecr, EIM_EXECUTED_COMMANDS eec where ecr.TRANSNO = eec.TRANSNO and ecr.SUBNO = '99006317' and ecr.EXCSYSTEM in ('ERIC','PROV') and (ecr.flex_fld2 <> 'BULK' or ecr.flex_fld2 is null) and ecr.TRANSSTATUS = 10 and not exists (SELECT 1 from EIM_COMMAND_RECORD ecr3 where ecr3.TRANSSTATUS in (20 , 47) and ecr3.subno=ecr.subno and ecr3.EXCSYSTEM in ('ERIC','PROV')) and rownum <=300 order by transno

NameValuePair.name: BusinessProcesses/Services/Provisioning/BMS-Poller/Query
NameValuePair.value: select /*+ INDEX (EIM_EXECUTED_COMMANDS SPC_TRANS_CMD_X1)*/ ecr.SUBNO SUBNO, ecr.TRANSNO TRANSNO, SUBSTR (TRIM (eec.command), 1, LENGTH (TRIM (eec.command)) - 1)||':TRANSNO,'||ecr.TRANSNO||';' command from EIM_COMMAND_RECORD ecr, EIM_EXECUTED_COMMANDS eec where ecr.TRANSNO = eec.TRANSNO and ecr.SUBNO in ('99690431' , '97798649' , '99006317' , '97128396') and ecr.EXCSYSTEM in ('ERIC','PROV') and ecr.exc in ('CCS1','CMS1','VMS3','STP','PURG','RBT1','MMS2','MCN1','AIR','BB1','GSM3','MNP1','BMS1') and ecr.SPC_FUNCTION not in ('WDR2','WGEN','WGN','WPVB') and (ecr.flex_fld2 <> 'BULK' or ecr.flex_fld2 is null) and ecr.TRANSSTATUS = 10 and not exists (SELECT 1 from EIM_COMMAND_RECORD ecr3 where ecr3.TRANSSTATUS = 20 and ecr3.subno=ecr.subno) and rownum <=300 order by transno

NameValuePair.name: BusinessProcesses/Services/Provisioning/BulkSmSPoller/Query
NameValuePair.value: select /*+ INDEX (EIM_EXECUTED_COMMANDS SPC_TRANS_CMD_X1)*/ ecr.SUBNO SUBNO, ecr.TRANSNO TRANSNO, SUBSTR (TRIM (eec.command), 1, LENGTH (TRIM (eec.command)) - 1)||':TRANSNO,'||ecr.TRANSNO||';' command from EIM_COMMAND_RECORD ecr, EIM_EXECUTED_COMMANDS eec where ecr.TRANSNO = eec.TRANSNO and ecr.SUBNO in ('99690431' , '97798649' , '99006317' , '97128396') and ecr.EXCSYSTEM in ('ERIC','PROV') and ecr.exc in ('CCS1','CMS1','VMS3','STP','PURG','RBT1','MMS2','MCN1','AIR','BB1','GSM3','MNP1','BMS1') and ecr.SPC_FUNCTION not in ('WDR2','WGEN','WGN','WPVB') and (ecr.flex_fld2 <> 'BULK' or ecr.flex_fld2 is null) and ecr.TRANSSTATUS = 10 and not exists (SELECT 1 from EIM_COMMAND_RECORD ecr3 where ecr3.TRANSSTATUS = 20 and ecr3.subno=ecr.subno) and rownum <=300 order by transno

NameValuePair.name: BusinessProcesses/Services/Provisioning/CADAE-Poller/Query
NameValuePair.value: select * from (select /*+ INDEX (EIM_EXECUTED_COMMANDS SPC_TRANS_CMD_X1)*/ ecr.SUBNO SUBNO, ecr.TRANSNO TRANSNO, SUBSTR (TRIM (eec.command), 1, LENGTH (TRIM (eec.command)) - 1)||':TRANSNO,'||ecr.TRANSNO||';' command from EIM_COMMAND_RECORD ecr, EIM_EXECUTED_COMMANDS eec where ecr.TRANSNO = eec.TRANSNO and ecr.SUBNO in ('99006317') and ecr.EXCSYSTEM in ('ERIC','PROV','SMS') and ecr.exc in ('CCS1','CMS1','VMS3','PURG','RBT1','MMS2','MCN1','AIR','BB1','GSM3','MNP1' , 'BMS1','SMS') and ecr.SPC_FUNCTION not in ('WDR2','WGEN','WGN','WPVB') and (ecr.flex_fld2 <> 'BULK' or ecr.flex_fld2 is null) and ecr.TRANSSTATUS = 10 and not exists (SELECT 1 from EIM_COMMAND_RECORD ecr3 where ecr3.TRANSSTATUS in (20 , 47) and ecr3.subno=ecr.subno and ecr3.EXCSYSTEM in ('SMS','ERIC','PROV')) order by transno) where rownum <=300
